&lt;ul>
&lt;li>&lt;a href="https://gohugo.io/installation/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Hugo（扩展版）&lt;/a>&lt;/li>
&lt;li>&lt;a href="https://git-scm.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Git&lt;/a>&lt;/li>
&lt;li>&lt;a href="https://go.dev/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Go&lt;/a>&lt;/li>
&lt;/ul>
